  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n1. create community\r\n2. mint owner token and token master token for it\r\n3. back up seed phrase\r\n4. delete your data folder and restart the app\r\n5. recover the account with the seed \r\n6. in the community that will be recovered for you, open overview page, airdrops page and tokens page\r\n\r\n**As result:**\r\n1. device is not recognised as control node\r\n2. there is Mint owner token on Airdrops page\r\n3. minting tokens is not possible\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/82375995/bd60cf79-a2c6-4f86-a190-a071787e8ecc\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1557\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-08-17 at 17 15 59\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/82375995/64a292f3-4262-4289-b006-e498340e9b94\">\r\n<img width=\"1557\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-08-17 at 17 16 05\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/82375995/ecea1712-83f3-43f8-abe3-b539ec48f7d1\">\r\n <img width=\"1557\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-08-17 at 17 16 19\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/82375995/43d1e2ee-f9fb-4c35-8d91-67407832b423\"> \r\n",
